com.hazelcast.core

Interface PostProcessingMapStore


  • public interface PostProcessingMapStore
    Implement this interface if you modify the value in MapStore.store(K key, V value) method. Otherwise already serialized form will be used to put into hazelcast map and modifications made inside store() method will be discarded. Applying changes done in store() is only possible with write-through configured map store.
